:

1. *Ma* da li ćeš doći na proslavu? (Will you come to the celebration?)
2. *Ma* kakav si ti čovek! (What kind of person are you!)
3. *Ma* li, znamo se dovoljno dugo. (Come on, we've known each other for long enough.)
4. *Ma*šala je očima i ismejala me. (She rolled her eyes and laughed at me.)
5. *Ma*šući mi rukom, poželeo mi je sreću. (He waved his hand at me and wished me luck.)
6. *Ma*lo je vremena pre nego što moramo da krenemo. (We have little time before we have to go.)